### Welcome to NetPHY Pages
The NetPHY website makes it easy to manage your router and any other kind of devices by offering everything you need in one place.

### Tech Tips Anyone?
We've crafted some great tech tips for you to use. Go ahead and continue to browse through them on our blog. https://netphy.wordpress.com/

### Rather Drive Stick?
If you prefer to live on the bleeding edge, go ahead and check out our website at https://sites.google.com/site/serialtips/. In addition to the blog, the Serial Tips website offers the latest news you may not find on the blog.

### Authors and Contributors
You can find us on GitHub @netphy and also on the support `links` below.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with some tips? Leave a comment on our blog https://netphy.wordpress.com/ or check out our Twitter page [@netphy](https://twitter.com/netphy), you contact us there and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
